You can say a lot about bts' music but i really gotta say that i never get tired of it. I can listen to them on shuffle a...
body:
You can say a lot about bts’ music but i really gotta say that i never get tired of it. I can listen to them on shuffle a thousand times and it won’t get old.

I spoil songs for myself a lot by listening to them over and over and once im done i will literally never listen to them again but bts is just….. constant…. always there…. never boring…. like i kid you not I’ve been listening to their their music for a good 3-4 years now and just……. still here…. still listing to all their songs…. esp forever young is just….. ethereal
